 count at seven consecutive Summer Games and looks to be a powerhouse again.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The U.S.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal count\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"seven consecutive Summer Games\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerhouse\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCU's coverage on iHeart's channels is expected to include Team USA men's and women's basketball, soccer, and volleyball, as well as swimming, gymnastics, track & field, and more.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 1694, \"end\": 1702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6914916774036257, \"rank\": 0.44614877182965573, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"iHeart's channels\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"volleyball\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are thrilled to partner with NBCU on coverage of the Paris Olympics this summer and heighten the excitement around this year's Games,\\\" saidMichael Biondo, President of Business Development and Strategic Partnerships.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 2036, \"entitie